#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:2
msgid "SSL/TLS"
msgstr "SSL/TLS"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:6
msgid ""
"SSL全称是Secure Sockets "
"Layer，安全套接字层，它是由网景公司(Netscape)在1994年时设计，主要用于Web的安全传输协议，目的是为网络通信提供机密性、认证性及数据完整性保障。如今，SSL已经成为互联网保密通信的工业标准。"
msgstr "SSL stands for Secure Sockets Layer. It was designed by Netscape in 1994 and is mainly used as a secure transport protocol for the Web. Its purpose is to provide confidentiality, authentication, and data integrity for network communication. Today, SSL has become an industry standard for confidential Internet communication."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:8
msgid ""
"SSL最初的几个版本(SSL 1.0、SSL2.0、SSL "
"3.0)由网景公司设计和维护，从3.1版本开始，SSL协议由因特网工程任务小组(IETF)正式接管，并更名为TLS(Transport Layer"
" Security)，发展至今已有TLS 1.0、TLS1.1、TLS1.2、TLS1.3这几个版本。"
msgstr "The earliest versions of SSL (SSL 1.0, SSL 2.0, and SSL 3.0) were designed and maintained by Netscape. Starting with version 3.1, the protocol was formally taken over by the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) and renamed TLS (Transport Layer Security). It has since evolved through TLS 1.0, TLS 1.1, TLS 1.2, and TLS 1.3."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:10
msgid ""
"如TLS名字所说，SSL/TLS协议仅保障传输层安全。同时，由于协议自身特性(数字证书机制)，SSL/TLS不能被用于保护多跳(multi-"
"hop)端到端通信，而只能保护点到点通信。"
msgstr "As the name TLS indicates, SSL/TLS only protects transport-layer security. At the same time, because of its own design, especially the digital certificate mechanism, SSL/TLS cannot protect multi-hop end-to-end communication and can only protect point-to-point communication."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:12
msgid "SSL/TLS协议能够提供的安全目标主要包括如下几个："
msgstr "The security goals provided by SSL/TLS mainly include the following:"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:14
msgid "认证性"
msgstr "Authentication"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:15
msgid "借助数字证书认证服务端端和客户端身份，防止身份伪造"
msgstr "Authenticate server and client identities with digital certificates to prevent identity forgery"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:16
msgid "机密性"
msgstr "Confidentiality"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:17
msgid "借助加密防止第三方窃听"
msgstr "Use encryption to prevent eavesdropping by third parties"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:18
msgid "完整性"
msgstr "Integrity"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:19
msgid "借助消息认证码(MAC)保障数据完整性，防止消息篡改"
msgstr "Use message authentication codes (MACs) to protect data integrity and prevent message tampering"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:20
msgid "重放保护"
msgstr "Replay Protection"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:21
msgid "通过使用隐式序列号防止重放攻击"
msgstr "Prevent replay attacks by using implicit sequence numbers"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:23
msgid "为了实现这些安全目标，SSL/TLS协议被设计为一个两阶段协议，分为握手阶段和应用阶段："
msgstr "To achieve these security goals, SSL/TLS is designed as a two-phase protocol, divided into a handshake phase and an application phase:"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:25
msgid ""
"握手阶段也称协商阶段，在这一阶段，客户端和服务端端会认证对方身份(依赖于PKI体系，利用数字证书进行身份认证)，并协商通信中使用的安全参数、密码套件以及MasterSecret。后续通信使用的所有密钥都是通过MasterSecret生成。"
" 在握手阶段完成后，进入应用阶段。在应用阶段通信双方使用握手阶段协商好的密钥进行安全通信。"
msgstr "The handshake phase, also called the negotiation phase, is where the client and server authenticate each other's identities (using digital certificates based on a PKI system) and negotiate the security parameters, cipher suite, and MasterSecret used for communication. All keys used in later communication are generated from the MasterSecret. After the handshake phase is complete, the protocol enters the application phase, where both sides communicate securely using the keys negotiated during the handshake."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:29
msgid "协议"
msgstr "Protocols"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:30
msgid "TLS 包含几个子协议，比较常用的有记录协议、警报协议、握手协议、变更密码规范协议等。"
msgstr "TLS contains several subprotocols. Common ones include the Record Protocol, Alert Protocol, Handshake Protocol, and Change Cipher Spec Protocol."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:33
msgid "记录协议"
msgstr "Record Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:34
msgid "记录协议(Record Protocol)规定了 TLS 收发数据的基本单位记录(record)。"
msgstr "The Record Protocol defines the record as the basic unit of data sent and received by TLS."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:37
msgid "警报协议"
msgstr "Alert Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:38
msgid "警报协议(Alert Protocol)用于提示协议交互过程出现错误。"
msgstr "The Alert Protocol is used to report errors that occur during protocol interaction."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:41
msgid "握手协议"
msgstr "Handshake Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:42
msgid ""
"握手协议(Handshake Protocol)是 TLS 里最复杂的子协议，在握手过程中协商 TLS "
"版本号、随机数、密码套件等信息，然后交换证书和密钥参数，最终双方协商得到会话密钥，用于后续的混合加密系统。"
msgstr "The Handshake Protocol is the most complex TLS subprotocol. During the handshake, it negotiates the TLS version, random values, cipher suites, and other information, then exchanges certificates and key parameters. Both sides ultimately negotiate a session key for the subsequent hybrid encryption system."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:45
msgid "变更密码规范协议"
msgstr "Change Cipher Spec Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:46
msgid "变更密码规范协议(Change Cipher Spec Protocol)是一个“通知”，告诉对方，后续的数据都将使用加密保护。"
msgstr "The Change Cipher Spec Protocol is a notification that tells the peer that subsequent data will be protected with encryption."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:49
msgid "交互过程"
msgstr "Interaction Flow"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:52
msgid "Client Hello"
msgstr "Client Hello"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:53
msgid ""
"Client Hello 由客户端发送，内容包括客户端的一个Unix时间戳(GMT Unix Time)、一些随机的字节(Random "
"Bytes)，还包括了客户端接受的算法类型(Cipher Suites)。"
msgstr "Client Hello is sent by the client. It contains a Unix timestamp (GMT Unix Time), some random bytes (Random Bytes), and the cipher suites accepted by the client."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:56
msgid "Server Hello"
msgstr "Server Hello"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:57
msgid "Server Hello 由服务端发送，内容包括服务端支持的算法类型、GMT Unix Time以及Random Bytes。"
msgstr "Server Hello is sent by the server. It contains the algorithm types supported by the server, GMT Unix Time, and Random Bytes."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:60
msgid "Certificate"
msgstr "Certificate"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:61
msgid ""
"由服务端或者客户端发送，发送方会会将自己的数字证书发送给接收方，由接收方进行证书验证，如果不通过的话，接收方会中断握手的过程。一般跟在Client"
" / Server Hello报文之后。"
msgstr "Sent by either the server or the client. The sender sends its digital certificate to the receiver, and the receiver verifies the certificate. If verification fails, the receiver interrupts the handshake. This message usually follows the Client Hello or Server Hello message."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:64
msgid "Server Key Exchange"
msgstr "Server Key Exchange"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:65
msgid "由服务端发送，将自己的公钥参数传输给了客户端，一般也和Server Hello与Certificate在一个TCP报文中。"
msgstr "Sent by the server to transmit its public-key parameters to the client. It is usually in the same TCP packet as Server Hello and Certificate."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:68
msgid "Server Hello Done"
msgstr "Server Hello Done"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:69
msgid "服务端发送，一般也和Server Hello、Certificate和Server Key Exchange在一个TCP报文中。"
msgstr "Sent by the server, usually in the same TCP packet as Server Hello, Certificate, and Server Key Exchange."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:72
msgid "Client Key Exchange"
msgstr "Client Key Exchange"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:73
msgid "客户端发送，向服务端发送自己的公钥参数，与服务端协商密钥。"
msgstr "Sent by the client to send its public-key parameters to the server and negotiate keys with the server."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:76
msgid "Change Cipher Spec"
msgstr "Change Cipher Spec"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:77
msgid "客户端或者服务端发送，紧跟着Key Exchange发送，代表自己生成了新的密钥，通知对方以后将更换密钥，使用新的密钥进行通信。"
msgstr "Sent by either the client or server immediately after Key Exchange. It indicates that a new key has been generated and notifies the peer that future communication will switch to the new key."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:80
msgid "Encrypted Handshake Message"
msgstr "Encrypted Handshake Message"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:81
msgid ""
"客户端或者服务端发送，紧跟着Key "
"Exchange发送。进行测试，一方用自己的刚刚生成的密钥加密一段固定的消息发送给对方，如果密钥协商正确无误的话，对方可以正确解密。"
msgstr "Sent by either the client or server immediately after Key Exchange. As a test, one side encrypts a fixed message with its newly generated key and sends it to the other side. If key negotiation is correct, the peer can decrypt it successfully."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:84
msgid "New Session Ticket"
msgstr "New Session Ticket"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:85
msgid "服务端发送，表示发起会话，在一段时间之内(超时时间到来之前)，双方都以刚刚交换的密钥进行通信。从这以后，加密通信正式开始。"
msgstr "Sent by the server to indicate that a session has been initiated. For a period of time, until the timeout is reached, both sides communicate using the newly exchanged keys. From this point on, encrypted communication formally begins."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:88
msgid "Application Data"
msgstr "Application Data"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:89
msgid "使用密钥交换协议协商出来的密钥加密的应用层的数据。"
msgstr "Application-layer data encrypted with the keys negotiated by the key exchange protocol."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:92
msgid "Encrypted Alert"
msgstr "Encrypted Alert"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:93
msgid "客户端或服务端发送，意味着加密通信因为某些原因需要中断，警告对方不要再发送敏感的数据。"
msgstr "Sent by the client or server to indicate that encrypted communication needs to be interrupted for some reason, warning the peer not to send more sensitive data."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:96
msgid "版本更新内容"
msgstr "Version Updates"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:99
msgid "TLS 1.3"
msgstr "TLS 1.3"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:100
msgid "引入了PSK作为新的密钥协商机制"
msgstr "Introduces PSK as a new key negotiation mechanism"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:101
msgid "支持 0-RTT 模式，以安全性降低为代价，在建立连接时节省了往返时间"
msgstr "Supports 0-RTT mode, saving round-trip time during connection establishment at the cost of reduced security"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:102
msgid "ServerHello 之后的所有握手消息采取了加密操作，可见明文减少"
msgstr "Encrypts all handshake messages after ServerHello, reducing visible plaintext"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:103
msgid "不再允许对加密报文进行压缩、不再允许双方发起重协商"
msgstr "No longer allows compression of encrypted messages or renegotiation initiated by either side"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:104
msgid "DSA 证书不再允许在 TLS 1.3 中使用"
msgstr "DSA certificates are no longer allowed in TLS 1.3"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:105
msgid "删除不安全的密码算法"
msgstr "Removes insecure cryptographic algorithms"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:106
msgid "RSA 密钥传输 - 不支持前向安全性"
msgstr "RSA key transport - does not support forward secrecy"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:107
msgid "CBC 模式密码 - 易受 BEAST 和 Lucky 13 攻击"
msgstr "CBC-mode ciphers - vulnerable to BEAST and Lucky 13 attacks"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:108
msgid "RC4 流密码 - 在 HTTPS 中使用并不安全"
msgstr "RC4 stream cipher - unsafe for use in HTTPS"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:109
msgid "SHA-1 哈希函数 - 建议以 SHA-2 取而代之"
msgstr "SHA-1 hash function - SHA-2 is recommended instead"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:110
msgid "任意 Diffie-Hellman 组- CVE-2016-0701 漏洞"
msgstr "Arbitrary Diffie-Hellman groups - CVE-2016-0701 vulnerability"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:111
msgid "输出密码 - 易受 FREAK 和 LogJam 攻击"
msgstr "Export ciphers - vulnerable to FREAK and LogJam attacks"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:114
msgid "子协议"
msgstr "Subprotocols"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:115
msgid "SSL/TLS协议有一个高度模块化的架构，分为很多子协议，主要是："
msgstr "SSL/TLS has a highly modular architecture and is divided into many subprotocols, mainly:"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:117
msgid "Handshake 协议"
msgstr "Handshake Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:118
msgid "包括协商安全参数和密码套件、服务端身份认证(客户端身份认证可选)、密钥交换"
msgstr "Includes negotiation of security parameters and cipher suites, server authentication, optional client authentication, and key exchange"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:119
msgid "ChangeCipherSpec 协议"
msgstr "ChangeCipherSpec Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:120
msgid "一条消息表明握手协议已经完成"
msgstr "A message indicating that the handshake protocol has completed"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:121
msgid "Alert 协议"
msgstr "Alert Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:122
msgid "对握手协议中一些异常的错误提醒，分为fatal和warning两个级别，fatal类型的错误会直接中断SSL链接，而warning级别的错误SSL链接仍可继续，只是会给出错误警告"
msgstr "Reports certain errors in the handshake protocol. Alerts are divided into fatal and warning levels: fatal errors directly terminate the SSL connection, while warning-level errors allow the SSL connection to continue but produce an error warning."

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:123
msgid "Record 协议"
msgstr "Record Protocol"

#: ../../source/network/ssl.rst:124
msgid "包括对消息的分段、压缩、消息认证和完整性保护、加密等"
msgstr "Includes message fragmentation, compression, message authentication and integrity protection, encryption, and related functions"

